{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-docs-tsx","path":"/0.6/docs/editor-viewport-cn","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/2517d654-a676-411e-b4bc-5dde6680786c/image-20210719155730830.png\" alt=\"image-20210719155730830\"></p>\n<p><strong>视图区</strong> 的主要作用是场景编辑，我们可以在这里布置所有的模型、灯光、特效等元素。并且可以选中模型用变换工具（Gizmo）去改变实体的位置（Position），旋转（Rotation）和缩放（Scale）。</p>\n<h2 id=\"编辑器相机操作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E5%99%A8%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"编辑器相机操作 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>编辑器相机操作</h2>\n<p>编辑器视口是由编辑器相机渲染的，通过操作编辑器相机可以实现场景的视角的调试。默认编辑器的相机模式是 3D 模式。</p>\n<h3 id=\"相机模式切换\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%9B%B8%E6%9C%BA%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%87%E6%8D%A2\" aria-label=\"相机模式切换 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>相机模式切换</h3>\n<p>我们可以通过按钮切换 2D/3D 模式：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/1230a461-1831-4551-9829-887ad476cedb/2D%3A3D.gif\" alt=\"2D:3D\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"3d-模式操作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3d-%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"3d 模式操作 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3D 模式操作</h3>\n<h4 id=\"旋转视角\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%97%8B%E8%BD%AC%E8%A7%86%E8%A7%92\" aria-label=\"旋转视角 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>旋转视角</h4>\n<p>按住<strong>鼠标左键</strong>拖动可以旋转视口：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/18607939-f6a6-48aa-885d-2905bd32df4e/3D-rotate.gif\" alt=\"3D-rotate\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"拉近远\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8B%89%E8%BF%91%E8%BF%9C\" aria-label=\"拉近远 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>拉近/远</h4>\n<p>滑动<strong>鼠标滚轮</strong>可以拉近/远视角：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/7e8fa18b-1406-453c-b3f3-f93da21eb708/3D-scale.gif\" alt=\"3D-scale\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2d-模式操作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2d-%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"2d 模式操作 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2D 模式操作</h3>\n<h4 id=\"移动视口\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E8%A7%86%E5%8F%A3\" aria-label=\"移动视口 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>移动视口</h4>\n<p>按住鼠标左键拖动可以移动视口：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/46acac8b-7ee8-455d-91d9-2af658b6065a/2D-translate.gif\" alt=\"2D-translate\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"拉近远-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8B%89%E8%BF%91%E8%BF%9C-1\" aria-label=\"拉近远 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>拉近/远</h4>\n<p><strong>滑动鼠标滚轮</strong>可以拉近/远视口：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/7afd7c10-4aa5-4fdb-a88c-7fe26e7f749c/2D-scale.gif\" alt=\"2D-scale\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"选中实体\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%AE%9E%E4%BD%93\" aria-label=\"选中实体 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>选中实体</h2>\n<p>场景中点击模型，出现包围盒和变换工具，inspector 出现对应实体的属性，表示选中了当前实体。点击空白区取消旋转。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/f08b07c3-226a-49be-af9c-b20c5951240a/select.gif\" alt=\"select\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"变换-gizmo-操作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%98%E6%8D%A2-gizmo-%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"变换 gizmo 操作 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>变换 Gizmo 操作</h2>\n<p>下面三个平移、旋转和缩放的工具，我们称为 Gizmo </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/c12ba611-324d-4f14-bf13-967f73a7c0cb/gizmo.gif\" alt=\"gizmo\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"平移\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B9%B3%E7%A7%BB\" aria-label=\"平移 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>平移</h3>\n<p>我们先需要选中实体，左侧状态栏选中平移按钮，平移 Gizmo 会出现在视图区。拖动不同的轴，可以往不同的方向移动物体。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/2337bbf7-b781-46b0-a57c-7a93d5f81ab7/gizmo-translate.gif\" alt=\"gizmo-translate\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"旋转\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%97%8B%E8%BD%AC\" aria-label=\"旋转 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>旋转</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/OasisHub/ff5bf975-11ed-481d-a220-73e3dad57fde/gizmo-rotate.gif\" alt=\"gizmo-rotate\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"缩放\" style=\"position:relative;\